Hi Paige,

 

I’m sorry I took so long to do so, but I’ve attached a response to your last post to me. Many thanks for it was quite helpful to me.

phone:  301 390 5115

Hi All,

 

I haven’t looked at Macbeth yet, but I plan to soon. I’ve replied to Paige’s Quikscript letter to me in the attachment. If anyone else would care to join in some beginning Quikscript correspondence with me, I’d like that.

 

Best Wishes,

 

 

e-mail: ed.gaddy@...

phone:  301 390 5115

I have attached an example of Junior and Senior Quikscript to this
post.  I had to use an attachment because I got sick of Windows crashing
all the time and switched to using Linux for my operating system.  I am
running Windows 98 in a window under Linux.  I haven't figured out how
to get Jerome into the Linux side of my computer yet.  (I'm not even
sure its possible since it is a truetype font.)

Paige Gabhart
